'''''Twelve Ton''''' was a [[Transport/Legends|transport]] in service of the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]] during the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]]. It was produced by the [[Contruum Shipyard|shipyards]] of [[Contruum/Legends|Contruum]], and named after an [[Twelve ton|animal]] of the world.<ref name="TUF">''[[The New Jedi Order: The Unifying Force]]''</ref>

